#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.44"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.44:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.44:0.2"
msgid "5. Cūḷavagga"
msgstr "5. The Lesser Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Kathāpavattisutta"
msgstr "44. When Conversation Flows"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.44:1.1"
msgid "“Tīhi, bhikkhave, ṭhānehi kathā pavattinī hoti."
msgstr "“In three situations, mendicants, conversation flows."

msgctxt "an3.44:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.44:1.3"
msgid "Yo dhammaṃ deseti so atthappaṭisaṃvedī ca hoti dhammappaṭisaṃvedī ca."
msgstr "When the teacher understands the meaning and the teaching."

msgctxt "an3.44:1.4"
msgid "Yo dhammaṃ suṇāti so atthappaṭisaṃvedī ca hoti dhammappaṭisaṃvedī ca."
msgstr "When the audience understands the meaning and the teaching."

msgctxt "an3.44:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yo ceva dhammaṃ deseti yo ca dhammaṃ suṇāti ubho atthappaṭisaṃvedino ca "
"honti dhammappaṭisaṃvedino ca."
msgstr ""
"When both the teacher and the audience understand the meaning and the "
"teaching."

msgctxt "an3.44:1.6"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi ṭhānehi kathā pavattinī hotī”ti."
msgstr "These are the three situations in which conversation flows.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.44:1.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
